{"tid":384382,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(魔禁三終於)三木一馬同川瀨浩平將於十月一日出席魔禁特別節目","createTime":"2017-09-02T09:04:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T17:51:48.000Z","uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28d7eeacb4cf05f48f743cc418b5763bf997bddb","tid":384382,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T09:04:26.000Z","msg":"三木一馬與川瀨浩平將出席日本動畫電視台Animax上的節目《アニカル部！ 》（Anime Culture Club），在特集「とあるシリーズ大解剖！」裡對魔禁作品進行全面性分析。<br />\n該特集將於2017年10月1日播放，與「電擊文庫秋之祭典 2017」同一天。<br />\nP/S：-<br />\n三木一馬：前電擊文庫編輯部總編兼《魔法禁書目錄》等其它輕小說作品的責任編輯。<br />\n川瀨浩平：動畫《魔法禁書目錄》I與II等其它作品的總製片者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64970ee7262e8bd76ae6e7183a5ff7294cce014b","tid":384382,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T09:05:14.000Z","msg":"出手機驚咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec58ae3a3a9ab64fc274076069306d56df019f19","tid":384382,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T09:07:09.000Z","msg":"佢出第三季我真係切咩都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d749c38d22fd9914d104337701c7e71304c30d90","tid":384382,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T09:11:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢出第三季我真係切咩都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nlm"},{"pid":"cba99ef1f046dc018b0f55bc40afc2f4f46f1706","tid":384382,"uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T09:13:36.000Z","msg":"樓主:假如刀劍三期動畫出先過魔禁三期 我即刻死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/156343/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/156343/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c286